## Import Requirements for Suppliers

International suppliers entering the German market must navigate specific requirements:

### Documentation

- CE marking recommended
- Quality certificates from accredited labs
- German language labeling
- Ingredient declarations in German

### Regulations

- EU REACH compliance for chemicals
- Food-grade certifications where applicable
- VAT: 19% (standard rate)
- Customs duty: 0% for charcoal

### Labeling Requirements

- German language mandatory
- Complete ingredient list
- Producer information
- Storage instructions
- Quality indicators

